Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到底到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於，那位大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限浩瀚的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻有數億的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿載著眾人的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有……惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認通往密羅奇尼的航線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航線287-56確認
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8號渦輪加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼事嗎，克勞德？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把資料拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這戰艦·卡路納斯的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛尼奇斯·J·肯尼提督是我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球聯邦軍裡\N沒人不知道我父親的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在[雷索尼亞行星之役]中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他巧妙地指揮僅有的7支部隊\N打了一場漂亮的勝仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並阻止了躲藏在雷索尼亞聯邦政府背後暗中操縱的\N法吉特行星傑·裏沃斯大帝的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年僅38歲就晉升為提督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都尊敬那樣的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次我以後備船員的身份\N初次和他坐上同一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且親眼目睹到他偉大之處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那寬闊的背影中充滿了他\N身為地球聯邦軍提督的威嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為這位英雄肯尼提督的兒子當我感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務是到密羅奇尼亞行星進行能量調查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近在該行星附近屢次發生原因不明的遇難事故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就要抵達目標宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離密羅奇尼亞還有20天文單位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航速減為正常速度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦屏障輸出功率提到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才抵達密羅奇尼亞的附近時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有探測到這樣的小行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底從哪裡冒出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分操控裝置發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功能恢復需要500秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，前面出現障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大型的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將與本艦衝撞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於操控裝置無法完全操作,來不急回避了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太巨大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種質量，防禦屏障無法抵擋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦與本艦衝撞……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦……將全毀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料上根本沒有那樣的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽電子炮發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標：接近中的大型小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來破壞目標所需要的能量充填\N至少需要250秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以陽電子炮為最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此要暫停正在使用的防禦系統\N以及船身控制系統的能量供給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦屏障解除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將全部能量集中到陽電子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船艦承受不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽電子炮的能量充填65%
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機房發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽電子引擎溫度異常驟升
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三雷射炮受損
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三區的生命維持機能已經降到三了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽電子引擎異常高溫,已經超過極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船艦會毀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽電子炮能量充填完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻破壞前方的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽電子炮發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人員準備接受衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一帶的數值又更高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是屬於磁能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從性質上的分析來看似乎不是磁能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然非常的相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們繼續調查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我解除屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得很莽撞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督的判斷…我認為非常正確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的話…我們現在恐怕……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽怯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來讓你到宇宙來還是太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量測定值是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法測定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船難事故一定和它脫離不了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍事武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有可能是哪個星系的軍事設備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡無法取得更進一步的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信它應該能夠保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的雷射槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎曾經在內部發生過巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有看過的這種形態的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨意的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會發生什麼事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快給我退下，不要在那裡礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是船上的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析這樣的裝置難不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個裝置……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送門，開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當世界充滿災禍使人們飽受苦難之時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自異世界的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將手持光之劍為我們消除災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,災禍……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您指的就是現在這個世界上所發生的……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不祥的現象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從巨大的隕石落下之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地異變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就出現了奇形怪狀的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傳說所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個勇者可以將我們從苦難中解救出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像傳說中所說的那樣就好了……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘到不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡路納斯…卡路納斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是克勞德·C·肯尼少尉，OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡路納斯，請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是克勞德·肯尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡路納斯 我是克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信器也不行……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是什麼地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩我一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊，兔子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有好幾年都沒有喝到這麼好喝的水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…會不會生我的氣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來讓你到宇宙來還是太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德·C·肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡！ 怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點趁現在逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會被幹掉的 你沒法跟他打的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來讓你到宇宙來還是太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽怯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終、終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最危險的時候救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜·藍佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德·C·肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只剩下這一朵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我為你摘的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與蕾娜的相遇也正是我冒險的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克勞德·C·肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我是傳說中的那個拯救這個世界的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞錯了，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索隕石並拯救你們的世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到原來的世界，我願望只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 星之海洋EX 遭遇（CONTACT）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不是什麼勇者
